quran[7{c,v,t}:
2,77,"aur kya yeh jantay nahi hain ke jo kuch yeh chupatay hain aur jo kuch zahir karte hain, Allah ko sab baton ki khabar hai"
2,78,"un mein aik dosra giroh ummiyunka hai, jo kitaab ka to ilm rakhtay nahi, bas apni be bunyaad umedon aur aarzouon ko liye baithy hain aur mehez vahm o gumaan par chalay ja rahay hain"
2,79,"pas halakat aur tabahi hai unn logon ke liye jo apne hathon se shara ka noshta likhte hain, phir logon se kehte hain ke yeh Allah ke paas se aaya howa hai taakay is ke muawzay mein thora sa faida haasil kar lain un ke hathon ka likha bhi un ke liye tabahi ka samaan hai aur un ki yeh kamaai bhi un ke liye mojab halakat"
2,80,"woh kehte hain ke dozakh ki aag hamein hargiz chone wali nahi illa yeh ke chund roz ki sazamil jaye to mil jaye inn se pucho, kya tum ne Allah se koi ehad le liya hai, jis ki khilaaf warzi woh nahi karsaktha? ya baat yeh hai ke tum Allah ke zimmay daal kar aisi baatein keh dete ho jin ke mutaliq tumhe ilm nahi hai ke uss ne un ka zimma liya hai? aakhir tumhe dozakh ki aag kyun nah chovay gi ?"
2,81,"jo bhi badi kamaye ga aur apni khata kaari ke chakkar mein para rahay ga, woh dozakhi hai aur dozakh hi mein woh hamesha rahay ga"
2,82,aur jo log imaan layein ge aur naik amal karen ge wohi janati hain aur jannat mein woh hamesha rahen ge
2,83,"yaad karo, Israel ki aulaad se Hum ne pukhta ehad liya tha ke Allah ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karna, maa baap ke sath, rishte daaron ke sath, yatimon aur miskeeno ke sath naik sulooq karna, logon se bhali baat kehna, namaz qaim karna aur zakat dena, magar thoray admion ke siwa ay tum sab is ehad se phir gay aur ab taq phiray hue ho"
